{"tid":36102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[廢老] 70歲老賊揸鎅刀 劫77歲伯伯1萬蚊","createTime":"2016-12-12T13:07:26.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T15:05:01.000Z","uid":122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"acfeff921ea370fa79b4622c672af97d6b987ba1","tid":36102,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T13:07:26.000Z","msg":"<strong>70歲老賊揸鎅刀 劫77歲伯伯1萬蚊</strong><br />\n<br />\n2016-12-12 20:44:00 HKT<br />\n<br />\n【20:44 更新】新增疑犯相片<br />\n<br />\n今早近11時，77歲姓黃的伯伯於香港仔利東邨東平樓乘搭升降機時，一名男子持鎅刀走近聲稱行劫，劫去黃伯約1萬元現金後，乘搭升降機逃去。警方將案件列作行劫，交由西區警區重案組第一隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n探員經調查後，下午於利東邨東昌樓拘捕一名70歲姓馬的老翁，涉嫌行劫，他現正被扣留調查。至晚上8時許，疑犯黑布蒙頭、雙手鎖上手扣由探員押返東昌樓搜屋，探員撿獲一批證物回署調查。"},{"pid":"be35f2d48932592ca46bec84d9c9185ce2b169ef","tid":36102,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T13:09:03.000Z","msg":"廢老大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a101cec66c60bc62193a740043ceed0b5e75d15","tid":36102,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T13:10:17.000Z","msg":"好心啲妹下妹下就係屋企休息下啦<br />\n七十歲重學人打劫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3aca04474005f68d2b4efabfc271b0fb4613e93","tid":36102,"uid":28892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T13:11:28.000Z","msg":"兩個都妹下妹下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52903f2a06ec82129aded18212408c8048d2c1fb","tid":36102,"uid":34949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T13:51:04.000Z","msg":"妹吓妹吓打劫妹吓妹吓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ca8b4f0d18c949da3ca488f87408db0c71a0cf","tid":36102,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T14:04:04.000Z","msg":"乘升降機逃去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla